<l n="1"><milestone unit="para"/>Huc omnes pariter venite capti,  </l>
            <l n="2">quos fallax ligat improbis catenis  </l>
            <l n="3">terrenas habitans libido mentes,  </l>
            <l n="4">haec erit vobis requies laborum,  </l>
            <l n="5">hic portus placida manens quiete </l>
            <l n="6">hoc patens unum miseris asylum.  </l>
            <l n="7">Non quicquid Tagus aureis harenis  </l>
            <l n="8">donat aut Hermus rutilante ripa  </l>
            <l n="9">aut Indus calido propinquus orbi  </l>
            <l n="10">candidis miscens virides lapillos, </l>
            <l n="11"><sic>inlustrent</sic> aciem magisque caecos </l>

